---
// CTA final · invitation directe, ton complice, pas pushy
---

<section class="py-24 md:py-32 px-4 relative overflow-hidden" style="background: #1a3d2e;">
  <!-- Décor : grosse pièce en arrière-plan -->
  <div class="absolute -right-32 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[500px] h-[500px] rounded-full opacity-[0.07] pointer-events-none" style="background: radial-gradient(circle, #f4c430 0%, transparent 65%);" data-parallax="0.05"></div>

  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto relative text-center">
    <p class="eyebrow mb-5 fade-up" style="color: #f4c430;">Allez, on y va</p>

    <h2 class="blur-reveal" style="color: #faf7f2; font-family: var(--font-display); font-weight: 700; font-size: clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 4rem); line-height: 1.05; max-width: 22ch; margin: 0 auto;">
      Calcule ton vrai budget.
      <span class="block italic mt-2" style="color: #f4c430; font-weight: 500;">Tu seras surpris.</span>
    </h2>

    <p class="mt-7 text-lg max-w-xl mx-auto fade-up" style="color: rgba(250, 247, 242, 0.85); transition-delay: 200ms;">
      Trois minutes pour savoir où passe vraiment ton argent. Et surtout, ce que tu peux vraiment changer.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 items-center justify-center fade-up" style="transition-delay: 350ms;">
      <a
        href="/calculateurs/budget-mensuel/"
        class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-semibold text-base hover-shine magnetic"
        style="background: #f4c430; color: #0f2419; box-shadow: 0 14px 32px -8px rgba(244, 196, 48, 0.45);"
      >
        Lancer le budget mensuel
        <svg class="w-4 h-4 transition-transform group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2.5">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3" />
        </svg>
      </a>
      <a
        href="/calculateurs/"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-base font-semibold border-b-2 pb-1"
        style="color: #faf7f2; border-color: rgba(250, 247, 242, 0.4);"
      >
        Ou voir les 11 autres
      </a>
    </div>

    <p class="margin-note text-base mt-8 inline-block" style="color: #f4c430; transform: rotate(0);">
      ✦ aucune inscription · aucun email · aucune banque rémunère ce site ✦
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
